The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 MacGill plea

Melbourne: Leg-spinner Stuart MacGill, who boycotted Australias last tour of Zimbabwe three years ago, has asked his teammates to take a closer look at the situation in the African nation. 

The world champions next assignment is a one-day series in Zimbabwe in September. 

Its naive to think that sport and politics dont mix, MacGill was quoted saying in an Australian daily. (PTI) 




